{"title":"Tensor","uid":"3cbc8b928d27cbb1d6d61c9b83fb1473","slug":"Tensor","date":"2021-09-16T12:01:39.000Z","updated":"2021-09-16T12:07:27.288Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Tensor.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109162005428.png","content":"<h1 id=\"pytorch入门\"><a href=\"#pytorch入门\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"pytorch入门\"></a>pytorch入门</h1><h2 id=\"Tensor（高维数组）\"><a href=\"#Tensor（高维数组）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Tensor（高维数组）\"></a>Tensor（高维数组）</h2><h3 id=\"Tensor的数据类型\"><a href=\"#Tensor的数据类型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Tensor的数据类型\"></a>Tensor的数据类型</h3><ul>\n<li><p>torch.FloatTensor ： 用于生成数据类型为浮点型的 Tensor ,传递给 torch.FloatTensor的参数可以是一个列表,也可以是一个维度值。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">import torch\na &#x3D; torch.FloatTensor(2,3)## 生成维度伟（2,）的浮点型Tensor\nb &#x3D; torch.FloatTensor([1,2,3,4,5])## 生成给定列表的浮点型Tensor\nprint(a)\nprint(b)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109160910273.png\" alt=\"image-20210916091047520\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>torch.IntTensor 用于生成数据类型为整型的 Tensor ,传递给 torch.IntTensor的参数可以是一个列表,也可以是一个维度值。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>torch.rand 用于生成数据类型为浮点型（0~1之间）且维度指定的随机 Tensor </p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.rand(2,3)\nprint(a)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109160913884.png\" alt=\"image-20210916091327733\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>torch.randn 用于生成数据类型为浮点型且维度指定的随机 Tensor,随机生成的浮点数的取值满足均值为 0 ,方差为1的正太分布。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)\nprint(a)</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109160917844.png\" alt=\"image-20210916091727216\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>torch.range 用于生成数据类型为浮点型且自定义起始范围和结束范围的 Tensor,所以传递给 torch.range 的参数有三个,分别是范围的起始值、范围的结束值和步长,其中,步长用于指定从起始值到结束值的每步的数据间隔，且range是包括右端点</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.range(1,20,1)\nprint(a)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109160923042.png\" alt=\"image-20210916092342637\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>尽量少用torch.range，将被移除，同时range是包括右端点，arange不包括</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.arange(1,20,1)\nprint(a)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109160927428.png\" alt=\"image-20210916092700209\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>torch.zeros 用于生成数据类型为浮点型且维度指定的Tensor,不过这个浮点型的Tensor中的元素值全部为0</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.zeros(2,3)\nprint(a)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109160929483.png\" alt=\"image-20210916092947264\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Tensor的运算\"><a href=\"#Tensor的运算\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Tensor的运算\"></a>Tensor的运算</h3><ul>\n<li><p>torch.abs 将Tensor类型的参数取绝对值输出</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)\nb &#x3D; torch.abs(a)\nprint(a)\nprint(b)\u0011</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161448862.png\" alt=\"image-20210916144834424\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>torch.add 求和，输入参数可以是全是Tensor数据类型的变量，也可以是一个Tensor，另一个标量</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)\nb &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)\nprint(a)\nprint(b)\nc &#x3D; torch.add(a,b)\nd &#x3D; torch.add(a,10)\nprint(c)\nprint(d)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161500326.png\" alt=\"image-20210916150055328\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>torch.div 求商，参数同上</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)b &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)print(a)print(b)c &#x3D; torch.div(a,b)d &#x3D; torch.div(a,10)print(c)print(d)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161525005.png\" alt=\"image-20210916152521694\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>torch.mul 求积，参数同上</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)b &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)print(a)print(b)c &#x3D; torch.mul(a,b)d &#x3D; torch.mul(a,10)print(c)print(d)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161527211.png\" alt=\"image-20210916152713795\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>torch.pow 求幂，参数同上</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)b &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)print(a)print(b)c &#x3D; torch.pow(a,b)d &#x3D; torch.pow(a,2)print(c)print(d)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161529579.png\" alt=\"image-20210916152946297\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>torch.clamp 对输入参数按照自定义的范围进行裁剪,大于上边界就重写为上边界，小于下边界就重写为下边界，最后将参数裁剪结果作为输出</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)\nb &#x3D; torch.clamp(a,-0.1,0.1)\nprint(a)\nprint(b)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161512855.png\" alt=\"image-20210916151246659\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>torch.mm 矩阵之间的乘法规则相乘，所以参数要满足矩阵乘法规则</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)\nb &#x3D; torch.randn(3,2)\nprint(a)\nprint(b)\nc &#x3D; torch.mm(a,b)\nprint(c)</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>​                <img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161536823.png\" alt=\"image-20210916153657676\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>torch.mv 矩阵和向量之间的乘法规则相乘，所以参数要满足矩阵和向量乘法规则</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a &#x3D; torch.randn(2,3)\nb &#x3D; torch.randn(3)\nprint(a)\nprint(b)\nc &#x3D; torch.mv(a,b)\nprint(c)</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161539489.png\" alt=\"image-20210916153936410\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","feature":true,"text":"pytorch入门Tensor（高维数组）Tensor的数据类型 torch.FloatTensor ： 用于生成数据类型为浮点型的 Tensor ,传递给 torch.FloatTensor的参数可以是一个列表,也可以是一个维度值。 import torch a &#x3D; ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.1k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Python.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Pytorch","slug":"Pytorch","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Pytorch.json"},{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Python.json"},{"name":"机器学习","slug":"机器学习","count":1,"path":"api/tags/机器学习.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#pytorch%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">pytorch入门</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Tensor%EF%BC%88%E9%AB%98%E7%BB%B4%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Tensor（高维数组）</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Tensor%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Tensor的数据类型</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Tensor%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Tensor的运算</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{}